<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<title></title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>Documentation for version: 0.0.4</h1>

		<h2>Root node: /api/</h2>

		<h3>Date format used (in request and response both) is YYYY-MM-DD</h3>

		<ul>
			<h3><li>End points</li></h3>
			<strong>Note:</strong> for all date related end points, if end_date is ommitted, it is taken as today. if start_date is ommitted it is taken as zero (problematic for present members as no members can be present before group was created).<br />
			<strong>Note:</strong> for period related end points, if start_date is ommitted, it is taken as date of first valid entry (no results are returned if no valid results found). if period is ommitted, it is taken as 1 day.<br />
			<strong>Note:</strong> if member-type is ommitted, all members are shown.<br />
			<strong>Note:</strong> values in &lt;&gt; are specific to the response needed and should be added without &lt; or &gt;.<br />
			<br />
			<ul>
				<h3>Root</h3>
				<li>/ : root node</li>
				<h3>Groups</h3>
				<li>/groups/ : list of all groups</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/ : details about a specific group</li>
				<h3>Group members</h3>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/members/ : details about number of members for the given group</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/members/new/?type=&lt;member-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;period=&lt;number-of-days&gt; : count of new members for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by join_time, separated by the given period</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/members/new/list/?type=&lt;member-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt; : list of new members for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by join_time</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/members/left/?type=&lt;member-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;period=&lt;number-of-days&gt; : count of left members for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by leave_time, separated by the given period</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/members/left/list/?type=&lt;member-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt; : list of left members for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by leave_time</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/members/present/?type=&lt;member-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;period=&lt;number-of-days&gt; : count of present members for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by join_time, separated by the given period</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/members/present/list/?type=&lt;member-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt; : list of present members for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by join_time</li>
				<h3>Group posts</h3>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/posts/ : details about number of posts for the given group</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/posts/new/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;period=&lt;number-of-days&gt; : count of new posts for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by time, separated by the given period</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/posts/total/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;period=&lt;number-of-days&gt; : count of total posts for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by time, separated by the given period</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/posts/list/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt; : list of posts for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by time</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/posts/by/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt; : number of posts by each user for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by number of posts (decreasing order)</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/posts/by/&lt;user-id&gt;/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt; : number of posts by the given user for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by time</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/posts/by/&lt;user-id&gt;/new/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;period=&lt;number-of-days&gt; : count of new posts by the given user for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by time, separated by the given period</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/posts/by/&lt;user-id&gt;/total/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;period=&lt;number-of-days&gt; : count of total posts by the given user for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by time, separated by the given period</li>
				<li>/groups/&lt;group-id&gt;/posts/by/&lt;user-id&gt;/list/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt; : list of posts by the given user for the given group, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by time</li>
				<h3>Users</h3>
				<li>/users/ : number of all users</li>
				<li>/users/&lt;user-id&gt;/ : details about a specific user</li>
				<h3>Posts</h3>
				<li>/posts/ : number of all posts</li>
				<li>/posts/&lt;post-id&gt;/ : details about a specific post</li>
				<li>/posts/by/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt; : number of posts by each user, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by number of posts (decreasing order)</li>
				<li>/posts/by/&lt;user-id&gt;/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt; : number of posts by the given user, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by time</li>
				<li>/posts/by/&lt;user-id&gt;/new/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;period=&lt;number-of-days&gt; : count of new posts by the given user, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by time, separated by the given period</li>
				<li>/posts/by/&lt;user-id&gt;/total/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;period=&lt;number-of-days&gt; : count of total posts by the given user, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by time, separated by the given period</li>
				<li>/posts/by/&lt;user-id&gt;/list/?type=&lt;post-type&gt;&amp;start_date=&lt;date&gt;&amp;end_date=&lt;date&gt; : list of posts by the given user, of the given type, within the given time period, sorted by time</li>
			</ul>

			<h3><li>Nodes</li></h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Group: {"id": group id, "name": group name, "created_on": date group created on}</li>
				<li>Member: {"id": user id, "name": user name, "join_time": time of joining group}</li>
				<li>User: {"id": user id, "name": user name, "is_page": is user a person or page, "join_time": facebook joining time, "friends": number of friends, "groups": number of groups, "lives": where the user lives, "works": where the user works (or page description if user is a page), "study": where the user studies}</li>
				<li>Post: {"id": post id, "group": group id, "user": user id, "time": time posted, "type": post type, "text": post text, "likes": likes, "shares": shares}</li>
				<li>Count: {"date": start date (end date is start date + period days), "count": number}</li>
			</ul>

			<h3><li>Acceptable values for member-type</li></h3>
			<ul>
				<li>creator</li>
				<li>admin</li>
				<li>moderator</li>
				<li>banned</li>
				<li><em>none</em> (all members)</li>
			</ul>

			<h3><li>Acceptable values for post-type</li></h3>
			<ul>
				<li>poll</li>
				<li>first</li>
				<li>link</li>
				<li>share</li>
				<li>with</li>
				<li>post (rest)</li>
				<li><em>none</em> (all posts)</li>
			</ul>
		</ul>
	</body>
</html>
